{"lemma":"نَقَلَة","slug":"نَقَلَة","root":"ن.ق.ل","root_slug":"ن-ق-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ق-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":11},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n44106"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to inform, to report","examples":[{"text":"قَالَ: «أَفَنَاقَلْتَهُ الْكَلَامَ وَفَاتَحْتَهُ الْأُمُورَ قَبْلَ أَنْ تُوصِلَهُ إِلَيَّ؟». قَالَ: «لَا»."}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active participle of نَقَلَ (naqala)","tags":["active","form-of","participle"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"mover, moving"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"transmitting"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"carrying, bearing"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"delivering"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"who quotes or cites"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"transporter"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"conductor"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"transmitter","examples":[{"text":"نَاقِل عَصَبِيّ","english":"a neurotransmitter"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"transmitter, vector (of disease)"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of نَقَلَ (naqala)."},"ipa":["/naː.qa.la/","/naː.qil/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n44106","headword_ar":"نَقَلَهُ","root":"nql","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He related it, told it, or mentioned it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"from another;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he transmitted it; he transcribed it."},{"kind":"text","text":"See 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HkY","text_ar":"حكى"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqala A_ilayohi HadiyvFA","text_ar":"نَقَلَ اـِلَيْهِ حَدِيثًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He related to him a tradition"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqalahu","text_ar":"نَقَلَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He transferred it; shifted it; translated it; conveyed it. He discerned it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took and mentioned it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely a word or phrase or signification, from ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn","text_ar":"من"},{"kind":"text","text":") such a one;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he quoted it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqalahu A_ilaY kitaAbihi mino kitaAbK A=xara","text_ar":"نَقَلَهُ اـِلَى كِتَابِهِ مِنْ كِتَابٍ ا=خَرَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he transferred it to his book from another book."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}